query:
DELETE FROM capital_budget_cycles
WHERE id IN (
  SELECT id FROM (
    SELECT c1.id
    FROM capital_budget_cycles c1
    WHERE EXISTS (
      SELECT 1 FROM capital_budget_cycles c2
      WHERE c2.name = c1.name 
      AND c2.startYear = c1.startYear 
      AND c2.endYear = c1.endYear
      AND c2.id < c1.id
    )
  ) AS duplicates
);
